title: Are You Being Duped? -  Kent Philpott epub/
description:
Are you being duped? is a book about countering error with truth. It is about discerning what we are really embracing when we believe certain ideas or philosophies and what the culmination of them will be. Be bold and read this book; if you do not think you are being deceived there should be no fear in being challenged, but if you are being duped and you do not realize it, this could be the most important book you have ever read.
